---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Support the project" description="Help MomentGraph process and review more source-grounded video knowledge.">
  <section class="support-hero"><div class="eyebrow">Support MomentGraph</div><h1>Help turn more lessons into usable knowledge.</h1><p>MomentGraph is an independent educational project. Financial support helps expand the source library while keeping every published claim traceable to reviewed transcript evidence.</p><a class="support-primary" href="https://ko-fi.com/tamasmartinec" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Support on Ko-fi <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span></a></section>
  <section class="support-use" aria-labelledby="support-use-title"><div><div class="section-kicker">What support enables</div><h2 id="support-use-title">More material, reviewed carefully</h2></div><ol><li><span>01</span><div><strong>Process more lessons</strong><p>Acquire captions and run structured concept extraction across additional public videos.</p></div></li><li><span>02</span><div><strong>Verify video moments</strong><p>Review footage so demonstrations point to the movement itself, not merely the spoken explanation.</p></div></li><li><span>03</span><div><strong>Improve the knowledge graph</strong><p>Consolidate concepts, connect related techniques, and maintain the open-source publishing pipeline.</p></div></li></ol></section>
  <section class="support-principle"><strong>Editorial independence remains unchanged.</strong><p>Financial support does not buy placement, approval, attribution, or favorable analysis. Published material must satisfy the same source and review rules.</p></section>
</BaseLayout>
